Package: com.colindavidr.amazondark
Name: AmazonDark
Version: 5.28.1
Architecture: iphoneos-arm64
Description: True dark mode for the Amazon Shopping app — a real dark theme, not a colour inversion. Dark Reader engine in web views, Amazon's own native dark theme for chrome, and a ported Dark Reader colour engine for native content. Product photos are never touched.
Maintainer: Colin Rioux
Author: Colin Rioux
Section: Tweaks
Depends: firmware (>= 15.0), mobilesubstrate, preferenceloader
Conflicts: com.yourname.amazondark
Replaces: com.yourname.amazondark
Homepage: https://github.com/colindavidr/Amazon-Dark
